      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CANYA ROMANCE (1) goes very well at this course having never missed the frame including 10 wins and three placings. Was out of placings last time (30.68) at Q Parklands in a OPEN, finishing eighth and beaten 14 lengths. Has the ability and looks a key chance here. DAYTONA SUNSET (2) is a talented type and proved too strong last time to win by 2.25 lengths at this track in a handy 25.62 beating Entertaining. Expected to measure up again. CANYA ATOMIC (4) put in a much better performance last start when in the placings at this track behind Wildash Jane (25.46) in a Grade 4/5. Has the pace to be prominent. The form out of the last run is proven to be strong. Can measure up. BURRINGBAR REBEL (8) was in the money last start and likely to feature again.",
